With displays up to 360Hz/QHD 240Hz, one may increase gaming speed while MSI’s Cooler Boost 5 technology keeps the system running smoothly.

This video with guide you through the features, hidden tricks, and also how to use these products. Enjoy!
#MSI #MSIGaming #GEseries #MSILaptopTutorial

node.text:
In this project, we wanted to showcase the Creator PS321QR monitor by building a custom river edge desk for it to live on! Unlike the many gaming monitors that MSI offers, the Creator PS321QR is catered to those who need image clarity and superb color accuracy. 

Equipped with a 2560x1440 resolution, flat Rapid IPS panel, this monitor covers 99% of both the sRGB and AdobeRGB color gamuts, 95% of DCI-P3, and even comes with a magnetic hood to help block out glares from ambient light! It even offers a 165Hz high refresh rate and a 1ms response time, making it no slouch when it comes to delivering a smooth, high framerate gaming experiencing.

To bring this custom river edge standing desk to life, we enlisted the help of DC Chavez. Not only did he tackle the regular challenges of building a river edge table with ease, but he was also able to build in some modern-day accessories anyone could use.

Check out more of DC’s work here: @dcchavez @grainbyember

node.title: River Edge Standing Desk - Creator PS321QR

PC specs:

MSI MEG Z490 ACE

Seasonic Focux GX-850 PSU

Corsair VENGEANCE RGB PRO - 64GB (4x16GB)

Corsair Force Series Gen.4 PCIe MP600 NVMe M.2 - 1 TB

Intel Core i7-10700K

MSI MAG CORELIQUID 360R

MSI GeForce RTX 2080 Ti GAMING C TRIO
